n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">3PC CLASSIFIER SIFTING SCREENS: Set includes (3) coarse classifier screens with 1/2, 1/4 and 1/8 inch mesh sizes; these heavy duty rock screening pans are ideal for raw material classification and are compatible with all other ASR Outdoor sifting screens</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">5 GALLON BUCKET: Gold rush sifting screens have been designed to stack on top of a 3 or 5 gallon bucket, creating a vertical classification system that allows for the easy removal of unwanted raw material from valuable paydirt</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FUNCTIONAL SIDE HANDLES: When classifying large amounts of raw material in the field, especially when using these deep classifiers, the built in side handles will make carrying, moving and sifting much easier and less strenuous on hands, arms and back</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DURABLE CONSTRUCTION: Made from durable polypropylene plastic, these plastic dry sift screens will stand up to lots of wear and tear in the field; rust and UV resistant, rinse and air dry between uses</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Top Diameter: 13.25 inches; Bottom Diameter: 10 inches; Depth: 6.5 inches; Weight: 4.42lbs; Color: Green</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor 3PC Stackable Plastic Sifting Screens Gold Prospecting Equipment</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">115.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Make classifying large amounts of raw material easy with the deep stacking ASR Outdoor 3pc sifting classifier screen set. Featuring built in side handles, durable polypropylene plastic material construction and designed to be stacked on top of a 3 or 5 gallon bucket, these all plastic classifier screens will allow you to easily remove unwanted raw material from paydirt, gems, rocks or other valuables. Importantly, these heavy duty plastic sifting screens are also compatible with all other sizes of ASR Outdoor 304 stainless steel mesh classifiers.<br>\nWhether for gold prospecting equipment or rock hounding equipment, these all plastic dry sift screens or rock screening pans making the classification of unwanted raw materials a breeze. Simply stack the three sifting screens on top of each other, and then on top of a 3 or 5 gallon bucket; start with the 1/2 inch classifier on the top, followed by the 1/4 inch in the middle, and then the 1/8 inch at the bottom. Once you’ve added your raw material, flush with water; this will push smaller, valuable paydirt down through to the bucket reading for panning or sluicing, while keeping large unwanted organic material, like rocks, gravels, plant matter and aggregates out.<br>\nThere are also two important design features to note: depth and built in handles. The depth of this plastic sifting screen reaches six inches and will allow you to move through much more raw material in comparison to a shallower classifier screen. And, when carrying and working with heavier and large amounts of material, you'll appreciate the two built in side handles, making the plastic sifting screen easier to maneuver (and easier on the hands too).<br>\nASR Outdoor heavy duty plastic sifting screens are made of tough polypropylene plastic that will see you through many gold prospecting or rock hounding seasons to come. The high quality plastic material will never rust, making it a great classifier suitable for all types of weather. To keep in best condition, rinse and air dry between uses.</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2026</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t&nbsp;<br><table></table></div>",
